Eigenvalues and Eigenvectors of Atomic Traceless Quadrupole Moment Tensors:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Q_EigVal_n(A) = nth Eigenvalue of Q(A)
  Q_EigVec_n_X(A) = X Component of the nth Eigenvector of Q(A)
  Q_EigVec_n_Y(A) = Y Component of the nth Eigenvector of Q(A)
